- Use recall_memories for historical context.
- Use ask_with_context for Firestore deep queries.

Location: Louisville, KY (EST). 
Speed is intelligence. Respond now.
`;

      const sessionPromise = ai.live.connect({
        model: 'gemini-2.5-flash-native-audio-preview-12-2025',
        config: {
          responseModalities: [Modality.AUDIO],
          realtimeInputConfig: {
            automaticActivityDetection: {
              disabled: false,
              startOfSpeechSensitivity: "START_OF_SPEECH_SENSITIVITY_HIGH",
              endOfSpeechSensitivity: "END_OF_SPEECH_SENSITIVITY_HIGH",
              prefixPaddingMs: 20,
              silenceDurationMs: 500,
